{"tid":1015380,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 唐詩詠初一孖教育界新歡行山 低調宣佈戀情？","createTime":"2019-02-10T02:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T18:42:49.000Z","uid":82917,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"25092d8949b2b26e2017cd206c966d85d45f9923","tid":1015380,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwsUekN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwsUekN.png&h=bcc0f26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐詩詠年初二突擊去了蕭正楠同黃翠如屋企拜年逗利是，但新正頭年初一呢？唐詩詠可能留了給一位好重要的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昨晚有位一向熱愛唐詩詠的網民發現</span></span>，唐詩詠年初二在ig貼相，留言年初一去了行山：「大年初一行個大運，享受陽光，享受寧靜。」唐詩詠坐在石欄上狀甚寫意，相當享受藍天白雲。不過翻查後，原來上年曾與唐詩詠傳過緋聞的升學顧問中心創辦人兼執行董事陳思銘（Samuel）（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2I242Y8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I242Y8&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=fcefb85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2I242Y8</a> ），早一日都有在ig貼相，tag了地點在小欖水塘，拍攝位置與唐詩詠一模一樣，同樣依靠相同的石欄拍照，恰巧兩人又是影單人相，誰人負責拍照頓成問號，似乎隱約宣佈豬年第一日就過了二人世界。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">該網名又高呼受情傷</span></span>，但唐詩詠其實多次講明現時有圈外追求者，又指正處於觀察期，考驗對方能否接受到她的工作時間，甚至不排除突然閃婚。至於唐詩詠上年被發現與Samuel食晚飯時，Samuel又摸頭又搭香肩，非常親暱，但唐詩詠當時否認拍拖，只回覆：「佢係我同林子萱嘅朋友，只係同朋友開心飯敍。」<br />\n<br />\n衰果真係呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/10/105256_bb47aa9bf004c6fd3cc4a8371d654bed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2F105256_bb47aa9bf004c6fd3cc4a8371d654bed.png&h=a4f89ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今鋪有人要就奉勸我姨正正經經，咪鬼再整色整水捆綁對方幫你煲新聞啦！"},{"pid":"06fed5cadfa28cdd8b133ba18cafa51098a66c7c","tid":1015380,"uid":82917,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[唐姨風暴] 震驚！唐詩詠認有追求者：唔講得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/988584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/988584</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b29d8bfa8f8a56cec07ed51450894b594184723","tid":1015380,"uid":49018,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"美人好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7305a889fd9f957143da0e7649bf3e8adc12e7e1","tid":1015380,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b29d8bfa8f8a56cec07ed51450894b594184723","tid":1015380,"uid":49018,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"美人好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"Mon post mon得咁實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知我屍會點回應？"},{"pid":"1c85a4834c0e236a957a1057d25469c49bce4502","tid":1015380,"uid":183383,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"屌乜春受情傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3773694170a7ba00eda4799d75e16a625b86f7","tid":1015380,"uid":183383,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"洪仔真係甩難喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616ce9ad9bbfa012927cced01845e276abf58c24","tid":1015380,"uid":82917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1c85a4834c0e236a957a1057d25469c49bce4502","tid":1015380,"uid":183383,"like":26,"dislike":1,"s